source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_00<tab>Woolnix is eyeing you with obvious interest.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_00<tab>Wollnix will dich auf den Prüfstand stellen.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_01<tab>Woolnix is fretting about the great swarm of tarantula hawks in the Collectors' Quarter. He does not feel safe guarding the gate whilst they are so near. Thus, he bids you slay three, in hopes that they will no more encroach upon his position.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_01<tab>Wollnix leidet unter den aggressiven <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20E09030402 /var> aus dem Manufaktur-Viertel. Vielleicht kannst du ihm zumindest drei Exemplare vom Hals schaffen.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_02<tab>You have struck down three tarantula hawks. Deliver tidings of your victory to Woolnix near the Cenotaph.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_02<tab>Du hast drei <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20E09030502 /var> besiegt. Berichte Wollnix am Zenotaph davon.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_03<tab>Woolnix reveals to you that he was stung by a tarantula hawk, and, driven mad by the pain, left his post. Now that there are a few less hovering about nearby, however, he believes he can do his duty in safety.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_SEQ_03<tab>Wollnix ist hocherfreut. Endlich kann er seinen Dienst ohne Angst versehen.

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_000<tab>Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Uplander has good arm for fighty-tool, yes?

TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_001<tab>Please, kill tarantula hawks for Woolnix. They are swarming in Collectors' Quarter, giving Woolnix terrible fright when gate guarding. Kill three, and Woolnix is feeling safer!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_001<tab>Wollnix kann nicht Gedanken zusammenbinden. Kommen Flattertier mit laute Flattern in Ohr ganzetag! Kannzu vielleicht aus Manufaktur-Viertel scheuchen? Dreistück <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20E09030202 /var>? Kho?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_010<tab>With so many tarantula hawks in Collectors' Quarter, Woolnix worried about gate guarding in safety.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_010<tab>Kannzu drei <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20E09030202 /var> aus Manufaktur-Viertel scheuchen? Wollnix wird haben große Dankenfühl in Herz für immerzeit.

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_020<tab>Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Uplander does great favor for Woolnix! In truth, Woolnix ran away when attacked by bugs. Woolnix was scolded for leaving gate unwatched, but this is unfair!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_020<tab>Khoo! Hazzu Flattertier besiegt? Wollnix wird halten Großwachsene<var 08 E905 (()) ((r)) /var> in Herz bis Sterbentag!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_021<tab>Woolnix was stung by tarantula hawk, ran because pain was driving Woolnix mad! <sigh> But now tarantula hawks are fewer, Woolnix can patrol in peace.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ801_01931_WOOLKNIX_000_021<tab>Jetzt kann Wollnix endlich Arbeit machen.
Kho? Was Arbeit ist?
Wollnix muss aufpassen mit Wacheauge und Flattertier scheuchen! Was hazzu denn glauben?
